  Phase III: The App Stores (Native Deployment)
  To get into the iOS App Store and Google Play Store, we utilize a "Hybrid-Native" strategy.


   1. Capacitor/Ionic Integration: We wrap your existing React code in Capacitor. This allows the exact same code to run as a "Native App."
   2. Native Sensors: We hook into the phone’s native capabilities (Haptic feedback for the zoom, Camera access for instant document scanning).
